pageContext.claim: “So we have a great governor in the state of Florida. Ron DeSantis. Calls me up -- doing a great job, Ron DeSantis. He was at three and he went to 70. That's a pretty good increase.”
pageContext.analysis: This is an exaggeration. DeSantis was polling in the teens in the Republican primary when Trump endorsed him and never had less than 9 percent support in public polling.
